description:
Demo.constructor(address[],address).multiSigWallet (contracts/DemoContract.sol#22) lacks a zero-check on :
		- s_multiSigWallet = multiSigWallet (contracts/DemoContract.sol#31)

Reentrancy in MultiSig.executeTx(uint256) (contracts/MultiSigContract.sol#191-207):
	External calls:
	- (success) = transaction.to.call{value: transaction.value}(transaction.data) (contracts/MultiSigContract.sol#202-204)
	Event emitted after the call(s):
	- TxExecuted(msg.sender,_nonce) (contracts/MultiSigContract.sol#206)

	Event emitted after the call(s):
	- [TxExecuted(msg.sender,_nonce)](contracts/MultiSigContract.sol#L206)
